          personal subscriptions, including cost, billing cycle, currency, category,
          and payment dates.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Analytics &amp; Insights</strong> — View dashboard analytics, monthly
          spending trends, cash flow projections, weekly renewal forecasts, and spending
          breakdowns by category and currency.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Push Notifications</strong> — Receive optional browser-based push
          notifications for upcoming payment reminders and subscription renewals.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Multi-Currency Support</strong> — Convert and display subscription
          costs in a preferred currency using exchange rate data.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>User Preferences</strong> — Customize currency, timezone, notification
          timing, and locale settings.
